trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SqlWorkflowInstanceStore"></xref> adds a default control endpoint using this class if the <<xref uid="langword_csharp_workflowInstanceControl" name="workflowInstanceControl" href=""></xref>> sub-element in the <<xref uid="langword_csharp_sqlWorkflowInstanceStoreBehavior" name="sqlWorkflowInstanceStoreBehavior" href=""></xref>> element is not specified explicitly.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SqlWorkflowInstanceStore"> </xref> legger til en standard kontrollen sluttpunktet ved hjelp av denne klassen hvis den < <xref uid="langword_csharp_workflowInstanceControl" name="workflowInstanceControl" href=""> </xref> > underelementet i den < <xref uid="langword_csharp_sqlWorkflowInstanceStoreBehavior" name="sqlWorkflowInstanceStoreBehavior" href=""> </xref> > elementet er ikke angitt eksplisitt.

trans-unit.source: The <`workflowInstanceControl`> sub-element in the SqlWorkflowInstanceStore element is an optional element that specifies parameters for a workflow instance control endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Den `workflowInstanceControl`> underelementet i SqlWorkflowInstanceStore-elementet er et valgfritt element som angir parametere for en arbeidsflyt forekomsten kontrollen sluttpunktet.

trans-unit.source: The Workflow Management Service uses this endpoint to issue control commands to the service host.
trans-unit.target: Arbeidsflyten Management-tjenesten bruker dette endepunktet til å gi kontrollkommandoer til Tjenesteverten.

trans-unit.source: If the <`workflowInstanceControl`> sub-element in the SqlWorkflowInstanceStore element is omitted, the SqlWorkflowInstanceStore still adds a default control endpoint using the WorkflowRuntimeEndpoint class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `workflowInstanceControl`> underelementet i elementet SqlWorkflowInstanceStore er utelatt, SqlWorkflowInstanceStore fortsatt legger til en standard kontrollen sluttpunktet ved hjelp av WorkflowRuntimeEndpoint-klassen.
